        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhy available-capacity a string, from the description of this property it is numeric value?\n\nAlso, p-interface -> service-instance edge is redundant, we already have pnf -> service-instance, we can traverse from p-interface -> pnf (parent) -> service-instance.",
